define({"topics" : [{"title":"Using Runtime Parameters","shortdesc":"\n               <p class=\"shortdesc\">Runtime parameters are parameters that you define in a pipeline and then call from         within that same pipeline. When\n                  you start the pipeline, you specify the parameter values to         use. Use runtime parameters to specify values for pipeline\n                  properties when you start the         pipeline.\n               </p>\n            ","href":"datacollector\/UserGuide\/Pipeline_Configuration\/RuntimeValues.html#concept_rjh_ntz_qr","attributes": {"data-id":"concept_rjh_ntz_qr",},"menu": {"hasChildren":true,},"tocID":"concept_rjh_ntz_qr-d46e20432","next":"concept_rjh_ntz_qr-d46e20432",},{"title":"Using Runtime Properties","shortdesc":"\n               <p class=\"shortdesc\">Runtime properties are properties that you define in a file local to the <span class=\"ph\">Data Collector</span> and call from     within a pipeline. With runtime properties, you can define different sets of values for     different <span class=\"ph\">Data Collector</span>s.\n               </p>\n            ","href":"datacollector\/UserGuide\/Pipeline_Configuration\/RuntimeValues.html#concept_fjx_g31_1s","attributes": {"data-id":"concept_fjx_g31_1s",},"menu": {"hasChildren":true,},"tocID":"concept_fjx_g31_1s-d46e20652","next":"concept_fjx_g31_1s-d46e20652",},{"title":"Using Runtime Resources","shortdesc":"\n               <p class=\"shortdesc\">Similar to runtime properties, runtime resources are values that you define in a file         local to the <span class=\"ph\">Data Collector</span> and         call from within a pipeline. But with runtime resources, you can restrict the permissions         for the files\n                  to secure sensitive information. Use runtime resources to load sensitive         information from files at runtime.\n               </p>\n            ","href":"datacollector\/UserGuide\/Pipeline_Configuration\/RuntimeValues.html#concept_bs4_5nm_2s","attributes": {"data-id":"concept_bs4_5nm_2s",},"menu": {"hasChildren":true,},"tocID":"concept_bs4_5nm_2s-d46e20915","next":"concept_bs4_5nm_2s-d46e20915",}]});